author: Julie Sherwood
title: Honeoye seeks Girls Varsity Basketball coach
text: Honeoye seeks Girls Varsity Basketball coach Honeoye Central School Athletic Program needs to hire a coach for the Girls Varsity Basketball team. Comment Posted Oct. 10, 2015 at 4:09 PM By Julie Sherwood Posted Oct. 10, 2015 at 4:09 PM Honeoye Central School Athletic Program needs to hire a coach for the Girls Varsity Basketball team. Interested candidates should send a letter of interest and resume by Oct. 19 to the school. Send letter and resume to Jennifer Green at Honeoye Central School, PO Box 170, Honeoye, NY 14471. (585) 229-4125 By Julie Sherwood
